code: @Override protected JndiRegistry createRegistry() throws Exception {     JndiRegistry jndi = super.createRegistry().     jndi.bind("myMap", myMap).     return jndi. }

@Test public void testMapPut() throws Exception {     assertEquals(0, myMap.size()).     template.sendBody("direct:start", "Hello World").     assertEquals(1, myMap.size()).     assertEquals("true", myMap.get("isMaster")). }
@Override public void configure() throws Exception {     from("direct:start").bean("myMap", "put('isMaster','true')"). }

@Override protected RouteBuilder createRouteBuilder() throws Exception {     return new RouteBuilder() {          @Override         public void configure() throws Exception {             from("direct:start").bean("myMap", "put('isMaster','true')").         }     }. }
